      "instructions": "Calculate the characteristic Unruh frequency (or temperature converted to frequency) associated with a cosmological acceleration $a \approx cH_0$. Use the formula $\omega_U = \frac{k_B T_U}{\hbar} = \frac{\hbar a}{k_B} \cdot \frac{k_B}{\hbar} = \frac{a}{c}$ (or equivalent dimensional analysis) to find the scale of the Unruh radiation frequency."
    },
