      "label": "calculate_compton_frequency",
      "instructions": "Express the Compton frequency of a particle $\omega_C = \frac{mc^2}{\hbar}$ in terms of fundamental constants and mass $m$."
    },
    {
      "label": "dimensional_gap_analysis",
      "instructions": "Compare the magnitude of the Unruh frequency $\omega_U \approx H_0$ with the Compton frequency $\omega_C$. Determine the ratio $\frac{\omega_C}{\omega_U}$ and identify the dimensional/magnitude gap between the cosmological scale (Hubble constant) and the particle scale (mass-energy)."
    }
  ],
  "synthesis_brief": "Combine the calculated Unruh frequency and Compton frequency to show that $\omega_C \gg \omega_U$ by many orders of magnitude. Use this massive discrepancy to conclude that resonance is impossible due to the extreme dimensional gap between particle-scale physics and cosmological-scale acceleration."
}
```

